text: Igor Patenko (born 25 May 1969) is a Soviet former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial at the 1992 Summer Olympics for the Unified Team. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani male cyclists Category:Soviet male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of the Unified Team Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Taraz
